data.description: Fantastic opportunity! Quaint 3 bedroom home with a large lot and great outdoor living space. 2 bedrooms down stairs with egress windows and large laundry room! Upstairs the master bedroom is conveniently located. Great office space or could be converted to an extra bedroom. Hardwood floors through the main level and beautiful natural light through your large bay window. In the Heart of Twin Falls this could be your new Home!
